what are ansible role
-->roles in ansible are next level of abstraction of ansible play book 

Benefits of using roles
-->idea of include file and combine them of form clean, reuseble abstraction
-->easy to maintain/troubleshooting  the play book 

structere of role

file : contains regular file those needs to copied to target host
handlers: event handlers
meta: role dependence 
templates: simler to file , but it contains dynamic data
tasks: playbook tasks
vae/group_var: varible defination